Door to door visits have launched in certain suburbs, while stationary vaccine sites in and around town are still available for both first and second doses to eligible citizens aged from 12 years and older. The following vaccination sites are available for this week in Middelburg: 10 – 15 January:
Middelburg Mall 10 – 14 January:
Wonderpark Spar
Adelaide Tambo Hall
Doornkop Clinic
eMhluzi Mall
Nasaret Clinic
Sr. Mashiteng Clinic (Mhluzi)
Rockdale Clinic Door to door visits:
The Department of Health will be offering door to door vaccination in Nasaret and Kwazamokuhle from 10 to 14 January.